Process called "perform_aes_gcm_encryption" that takes plaintext as String and key as String and nonce as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_aes_gcm_decryption" that takes ciphertext as String and key as String and nonce as String and tag as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_chacha20_poly1305_encryption" that takes plaintext as String and key as String and nonce as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_chacha20_poly1305_decryption" that takes ciphertext as String and key as String and nonce as String and tag as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_xchacha20_poly1305_encryption" that takes plaintext as String and key as String and nonce as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_xchacha20_poly1305_decryption" that takes ciphertext as String and key as String and nonce as String and tag as String returns Dictionary

Note: Key Generation Functions
Process called "perform_keypair_generation" that takes algorithm as KeyExchangeAlgorithm returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_hkdf_derivation" that takes key_material as String and context as String and length as Integer returns String

Note: Key Exchange Implementation Functions
Process called "perform_ecdh_p256" that takes private_key as String and public_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_x25519" that takes private_key as String and public_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_dhe_2048" that takes private_key as String and public_key as String returns Dictionary

Note: Hashing Functions
Process called "hash_data" that takes data as Any and algorithm as String returns String

Note: Signature Implementation Functions
Process called "perform_ecdsa_p256_sign" that takes data_hash as String and private_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_ecdsa_p256_verify" that takes data_hash as String and signature as String and public_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_ed25519_sign" that takes data_hash as String and private_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_ed25519_verify" that takes data_hash as String and signature as String and public_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_rsa_pss_sign" that takes data_hash as String and private_key as String returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_rsa_pss_verify" that takes data_hash as String and signature as String and public_key as String returns Dictionary

Note: Key Derivation Functions
Process called "derive_master_key_from_shared_secret" that takes shared_secret as String and agent1 as String and agent2 as String returns CryptoKey

Note: Security Context Functions
Process called "create_failed_security_context" that takes context_id as String and error_message as String returns SecurityContext

Note: Certificate Functions
Process called "sign_certificate" that takes certificate_data as Dictionary and private_key as CryptoKey returns String
Process called "calculate_certificate_fingerprint" that takes certificate_data as Dictionary returns String
Process called "verify_certificate_signature" that takes certificate as CertificateInfo and ca_key as CryptoKey returns Dictionary

Note: Audit Functions
Process called "format_audit_log_entry" that takes log_entry as SecurityAuditLog returns String

